'''Pringle's puffback''' ('''''Dryoscopus pringlii''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Malaconotidae]]. It is found in southern [[Ethiopia]], [[Kenya]], [[Somalia]], and northern [[Tanzania]]. Its natural [[habitat]] is dry [[savanna]].

